Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.20,Narration,,0,0,0,,This might seem like a fairytale,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:44.46,Narration,,0,0,0,,you might even laugh from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:48.86,Narration,,0,0,0,,You will say that something so strange is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:33.00,Narration,,0,0,0,,But this is certainly my mother's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:37.44,Narration,,0,0,0,,The person my mother fell in love with,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:40.22,Narration,,0,0,0,,was a wolf-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:09.86,Narration,,0,0,0,,My mother was a student in a national university on the outskirts of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.98,Narration,,0,0,0,,Her scholarship covered her school fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.64,Narration,,0,0,0,,And for her living expenses she had a part-time job at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who are praised by their wisdom in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly had a vast knowledge of not only his own field,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but also on miscellaneous subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But about the true, the good, and the beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,they had no knowledge about Areté.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:37.52,Narration,,0,0,0,,In an early summer day, my mom saw my father for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:40.42,Narration,,0,0,0,,He was wearing a T-shirt with a wide collar,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:44.94,Narration,,0,0,0,,taking notes without a textbook on nothing but a notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:48.42,Narration,,0,0,0,,She thought he was very different from the other students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the attendance ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't sign and turn it in you won't be marked present.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a student here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm an eyesore, I won't be coming again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you're a student or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but at that lecture you didn't have a textbook so I thought it would be a bit hard to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we share mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be done by Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be careful with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I place this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The three complainants of this trial were the poet Meletus,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,an important man with strong political force called Anytus,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sophist Lycon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The representative was Melutus, but Anytus was the one behind the prosecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do for fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of food do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person do you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you called “Hana”?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was born the cosmos flowers in the backyard were blooming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't plant them, they were blooming naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When my father saw them he immediately thought:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,“I will raise my kid to have a smile beautiful as a flower, that won't fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether faced with difficulties or suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we will smile, whether we feel like it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll be able to overcome almost anything.”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, at my fathers funeral, I was smiling the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My relatives were all thinking “What an indiscretion”.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That made me really angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Maybe that was an indiscretion after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the same multi-unit apartments, but each one is different inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There are homes with money, and those without,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,homes with lots of family, and single households,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,homes with babies, and homes with only elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be nice to have a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying “I'm home” when you arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Remove your shoes, wash your face and hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and sit yourself comfortably on a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I would build a shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fill it with books and then build another shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You could do as you please,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,your own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll say “Welcome home” when you arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I must tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:10:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something I never told anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because you might leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I should have told you sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I should have shown you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shown me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you close your eyes for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I open them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.40,Narration,,0,0,0,,Transforming on full-moon nights,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:16.94,Narration,,0,0,0,,and attacking people was known as just a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:21.10,Narration,,0,0,0,,The world is full of things unknown to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:25.00,Narration,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's probably what my mother thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I shock you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we stop meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're trembling. Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:57.20,Narration,,0,0,0,,My father was a descendant of the Japanese wolves,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:59.20,Narration,,0,0,0,,that went extinct about a hundred years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:04.98,Narration,,0,0,0,,The last being that inherited a blood mix of humans and wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:11.78,Narration,,0,0,0,,His parents told him, when he was still very young, the history of their family's destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:15.72,Narration,,0,0,0,,They told him that the truth should not be revealed, and died after.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:20.42,Narration,,0,0,0,,He was then left in the care of relatives that knew nothing about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.42,Narration,,0,0,0,,faced many troubles and grew up into an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:27.84,Narration,,0,0,0,,He got a driver's license and moved to the city to look for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:32.44,Narration,,0,0,0,,He knew no one, and had no one to look back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:36.46,Narration,,0,0,0,,Until that point he had taken care to live in secret and in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:38.56,Narration,,0,0,0,,That's what my father said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gentle to Heart and Body\NNatural Birth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.94,Narration,,0,0,0,,Mom gave birth to me in that small apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:35.92,Narration,,0,0,0,,It was a snowy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:40.14,Narration,,0,0,0,,Without a hospital or even the help of a midwife,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.44,Narration,,0,0,0,,only by themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:45.56,Narration,,0,0,0,,My mother was really worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:50.28,Narration,,0,0,0,,that if I was born as a wolf, the doctors would be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad she was born safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:18:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But things are just starting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she grow to be a gentle child?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She will probably be a very smart kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of adult she'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Weather a nurse, a teacher, or a baker,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I want her to work on whatever she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to raise her without any thoughts of hardship,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to become a happy and healthy child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll watch over her until she grows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:43.96,Narration,,0,0,0,,My little brother was born in the spring of the following year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.86,Narration,,0,0,0,,It was a rainy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:51.28,Narration,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, my father had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:42.66,Narration,,0,0,0,,I don't know... what my father was thinking that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:47.78,Narration,,0,0,0,,It was probably the instinct of hunting food for the baby at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:52.48,Narration,,0,0,0,,He probably just wanted to give my mother, who had just given birth, something nutritious to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[TN: That's a driving license]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:58.04,Narration,,0,0,0,,I leave the children in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:02.84,Narration,,0,0,0,,My mother heard it like he said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll raise them well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:25.32,Narration,,0,0,0,,After that I don't remember my mother ever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.50,Narration,,0,0,0,,thinking about anything serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making it now. Wait a bit longer, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.60,0:22:39.36,Narration,,0,0,0,,She said that whenever I got angry and grumbled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:42.64,Narration,,0,0,0,,my fur would grow out and I would turn into a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a biscuit before lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:54.74,Narration,,0,0,0,,It seems I used to eat a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.74,0:22:58.16,Narration,,0,0,0,,crying out and searching for food from morning until night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:02.66,Narration,,0,0,0,,I was very different from my brother who ate little and was weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:08.54,Narration,,0,0,0,,My mother took a suspension from college to raise us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:10.38,Narration,,0,0,0,,She also had to quit her part time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:19.42,Narration,,0,0,0,,The small savings my father left us were enough to sustain our living.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:34.18,Narration,,0,0,0,,According our mother, she was wondering whether
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:38.22,Narration,,0,0,0,,to have us live as humans or wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:40.76,Narration,,0,0,0,,She was at a loss over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.66,0:23:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:57.92,Narration,,0,0,0,,It's not like our mother could discuss it with the neighbors,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:24:00.62,Narration,,0,0,0,,so she had to study everything by herself in books.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:04.12,Narration,,0,0,0,,Day or night, she had to breastfeed for two whole hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:10.12,Narration,,0,0,0,,Whenever her breast didn't produce milk she used skim milk instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.14,0:24:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Living with Wolves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.72,0:24:25.12,Narration,,0,0,0,,But when he wasn't hungry but was still crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.12,0:24:26.82,Narration,,0,0,0,,without knowing what to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.82,0:24:30.00,Narration,,0,0,0,,she stayed up all night holding him and caressing his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.22,0:24:35.74,Narration,,0,0,0,,Because of that my mother would always be dozing off once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.58,0:24:47.76,Narration,,0,0,0,,Because of that she was always falling asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.76,0:24:49.96,Narration,,0,0,0,,even if she just closed her eyes for a short moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.94,0:24:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.64,0:24:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.08,0:25:00.86,Narration,,0,0,0,,The problem was when we got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.50,0:25:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.40,0:25:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.26,0:25:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:22.16,Narration,,0,0,0,,She was conflicted between going to the pediatrics or the vets...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.10,0:25:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My child ended up eating drying agent by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.56,0:25:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She is two years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.68,0:25:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she vomited.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.04,0:25:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no blood in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.26,0:25:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It has “Silica Gel” written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.88,0:25:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Are there any complications?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.74,0:25:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Her appetite?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.88,0:25:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.04,0:25:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.30,0:25:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.28,0:25:51.84,Narration,,0,0,0,,My mother regrets never asking how my father was raised when he was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.48,0:25:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.40,0:25:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.48,0:25:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.42,0:25:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been in bad health the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.82,0:25:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So we...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.58,0:25:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,WALK!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.56,0:26:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it. Gee...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.82,0:26:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hide your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.22,0:26:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.84,0:26:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But watch your ears! They are showing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.28,0:26:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.82,0:26:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon. How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.86,0:26:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice, he called you cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.88,0:26:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,S- sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.98,0:26:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.00,0:26:57.22,Narration,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't the only problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.20,0:27:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What time do you think it is? Stop with the noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.44,0:27:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.46,0:27:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single night it's the same thing, for crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.06,0:27:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.36,0:27:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach them some discipline!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.90,0:27:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there. It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.10,0:27:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written in the lease that pets are prohibited in the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.44,0:27:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.70,0:27:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.24,0:27:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find out about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.40,0:27:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright? If you do things your own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.54,0:27:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you're more than welcome to go someplace else you prefer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.38,0:28:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,From the child consultation center?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.76,0:28:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the neighbors are worried the children are in peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.26,0:28:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.88,0:28:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Our research shows your children never had a medical checkup
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.08,0:28:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,or went through immunization, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.94,0:28:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. They are healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.28,0:28:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's okay, we would at least like to take a look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.48,0:28:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.56,0:28:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.74,0:28:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It is just to confirm what you are saying is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.92,0:28:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,T- that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.60,0:28:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up, we'll have no choice but to suspect you of ill-treatment and neglect.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.92,0:28:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.24,0:29:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Slooow!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.28,0:29:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.24,0:29:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What, mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.18,0:29:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.70,0:29:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To be human, or wolves?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.46,0:29:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.82,0:29:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to someplace you can choose whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.88,0:29:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start with the vacant houses by the town hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.32,0:29:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We gradually get more people saying they want to live a country life,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.48,0:30:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but they don't stay long.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.98,0:30:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, there isn't much around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.42,0:30:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The elementary schools and hospitals are 30 minutes away by car,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.16,0:30:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and if they're in middle school, it's a two and a half hour one-way bus and train ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.62,0:30:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A round trip is five hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.56,0:30:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say you want to raise your kids in a good environment...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.88,0:30:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say the city is a much more convenient place.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.00,0:30:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.22,0:30:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the rent makes this place seem almost free,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.76,0:30:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the price for repairs would be insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.72,0:30:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's an abandoned house...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.02,0:30:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's okay to keep your shoes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.94,0:30:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is practically dilapidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.48,0:30:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least the electricity still works.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.30,0:30:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the stream water hasn't dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.70,0:30:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And the things from the shed are also okay to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.98,0:30:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a field, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.56,0:31:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this place is not suited for self-sufficiency.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.48,0:31:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Animals come down from the mountain and damage the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.78,0:31:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you took the time to plant vegetables, they'd just eat them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.06,0:31:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The houses in this area became empty because
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.74,0:31:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the humans around here were driven out by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.04,0:31:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So the neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.84,0:31:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Neighborhood? No one ever comes down so you won't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.52,0:31:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to see someplace else?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.64,0:31:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Around the village would be more practical...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.20,0:31:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.08,0:31:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.44,0:31:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.64,0:31:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.54,0:31:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.80,0:31:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our new house.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.72,0:31:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's slanting!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.58,0:31:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, ants!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.00,0:31:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.12,0:32:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Step! Step!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.44,0:32:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.70,0:32:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Do you guys like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.16,0:32:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.02,0:32:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.52,0:32:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted someplace where there was nobody living around.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.08,0:32:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a bit eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.56,0:32:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And her husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.34,0:32:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.24,0:32:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Any income?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.26,0:32:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.02,0:32:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So how does she plan on providing for her and her children?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.82,0:32:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps Nirasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.52,0:32:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be gentle on them this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.36,0:33:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,3... 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.58,0:33:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look. Mom, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.84,0:33:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come down. Come down. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.52,0:33:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, come. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.12,0:34:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame, Age 4
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.12,0:34:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, Age 5
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.58,0:34:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.02,0:34:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.80,0:35:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.94,0:35:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.14,0:35:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.18,0:35:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the woman from the rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.90,0:35:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on I'll have to start saving as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.62,0:35:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,S-a-v-i-n-g?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.60,0:35:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we will have to do things like planting our own vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.16,0:35:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.52,0:35:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.62,0:35:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.58,0:35:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.50,0:35:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.76,0:35:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.36,0:35:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.88,0:36:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki and Ame being wolf children is our little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.38,0:36:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.56,0:36:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If they suddenly transformed into wolves,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.54,0:36:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone would be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.84,0:36:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they could never turn into wolves in front of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.86,0:36:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? It's our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.40,0:36:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.04,0:36:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.66,0:36:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever meet an animal on the mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.90,0:36:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,don't be arrogant with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.50,0:36:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.08,0:36:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that would make you father sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.64,0:36:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? You get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.08,0:36:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.04,0:36:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,“We won't forgive you!” said the very angry\Nvillagers as they chased the wolf with their guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.28,0:36:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,“I'm sorry! I won't do it anymore” cried the boasting wolf while running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.22,0:37:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.28,0:37:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why indeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.66,0:37:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.68,0:37:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.12,0:37:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,May I take the fallen leaves from the woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.80,0:37:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.16,0:37:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The fallen leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.74,0:37:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to ask anybody to take those.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.68,0:37:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.54,0:37:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will she keep it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.30,0:37:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She has been quite the talk around the\N convenience store and the karaoke place.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.16,0:37:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.82,0:37:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This time for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.62,0:37:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.00,0:37:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.84,0:37:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A tortoiseshell cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.28,0:38:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he's a wolf, it had its eyes on him since he's weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.18,0:38:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are just scratches.  They are nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.16,0:38:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't survive with those!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.94,0:38:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.92,0:38:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you comfort me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.16,0:38:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be alright. You sure will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.76,0:38:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki would never lose, not even for a boar!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.30,0:38:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw a boar?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.58,0:38:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I did! I also saw a monkey and a wild goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.02,0:38:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't scared at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.88,0:38:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun when I started chasing them and they ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.40,0:38:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Also-
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.06,0:38:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.02,0:38:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, when I peed...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.10,0:38:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.30,0:38:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't be self-important around other animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.98,0:38:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.12,0:38:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.80,0:38:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okaaay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.54,0:38:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.44,0:38:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you comfort me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.30,0:38:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be alright, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.90,0:38:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.38,0:38:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How does a wolf child become an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.90,0:38:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki! Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.68,0:38:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.10,0:38:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.94,0:39:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're slow. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.20,0:39:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolves start hunting only four months after they are born.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.78,0:39:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,First they start with small game like rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.10,0:39:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When they grow up, they team up with adult wolves and...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.44,0:39:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,TEAM!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.48,0:39:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.88,0:39:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.62,0:39:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go too far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.38,0:39:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.30,0:39:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.84,0:39:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.38,0:39:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we can eat this plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.64,0:39:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.20,0:39:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.02,0:39:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.80,0:40:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, look Ame.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.80,0:40:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. It will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.72,0:40:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.32,0:40:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great cormorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.32,0:40:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a stream on the other side and...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.58,0:40:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.00,0:40:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are wolves always the bad guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.88,0:40:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because... of that picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.04,0:40:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone hates him and he gets killed at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.28,0:40:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.82,0:40:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate being a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.08,0:40:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.16,0:40:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.42,0:40:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother loves wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.82,0:40:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if everyone else hates them,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.68,0:40:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,your mother is their friends, even if just by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.06,0:41:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Moom. Mooom.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.86,0:41:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.90,0:41:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They are withering again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.02,0:41:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.14,0:41:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.02,0:41:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.18,0:41:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.58,0:41:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.82,0:41:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use. Your mother still has to study much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.44,0:41:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you help me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.46,0:41:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.86,0:41:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.42,0:41:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.34,0:41:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.46,0:41:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.14,0:41:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about greeting you at your home,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.62,0:41:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but with all the commotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.20,0:41:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Growing food is harder than it looks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.18,0:41:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I did everything in the books it just ends up failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.98,0:41:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a great place, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.10,0:42:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Full of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.16,0:42:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so natural?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.70,0:42:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What you planted today won't grow tomorrow, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.14,0:42:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times you plant it, it's always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.72,0:42:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you were thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.62,0:42:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,T- that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.84,0:42:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.62,0:42:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.26,0:42:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiling won't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.32,0:42:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.78,0:42:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I don't know how to do this and I'm hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.52,0:42:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you're an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.62,0:42:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret not asking your father about more various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.40,0:43:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. So bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.88,0:43:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.90,0:43:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um....
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.26,0:43:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. This is to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.98,0:43:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.22,0:43:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Seed potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.54,0:43:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And you plant these in the fields?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.42,0:43:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use it to do many more things.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.98,0:43:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The old man told me about it, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.56,0:43:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just his personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.12,0:43:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.96,0:43:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.68,0:43:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.04,0:43:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.02,0:43:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.18,0:43:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man Nirasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.04,0:43:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the seed potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.10,0:43:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you plan to let them go to waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.42,0:43:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Start over from the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.32,0:44:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't dig like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.20,0:44:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.34,0:44:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... What about fertilizers?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.36,0:44:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bury the dry leaves there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.14,0:44:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.94,0:44:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.66,0:44:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're done, work the soil up here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.92,0:44:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't need to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.86,0:44:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just for me and my two children to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.20,0:44:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.94,0:44:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.52,0:45:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Create the rows.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.18,0:45:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.78,0:45:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave more space between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.04,0:45:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.72,0:45:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too low, make them higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.66,0:45:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.12,0:46:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In one week, plant the cut part facing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.62,0:46:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't add water or anything, just leave them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.22,0:46:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Thanks for teaching me so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.38,0:46:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.82,0:46:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.88,0:46:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.18,0:46:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.78,0:46:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, just come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.66,0:46:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.20,0:46:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.56,0:47:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.90,0:47:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.62,0:47:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are chamomile and cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.44,0:47:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you plant them together, it will make a taste bugs don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.22,0:47:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.08,0:47:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Celery is much better with cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.28,0:47:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.42,0:47:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For beginners this is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.78,0:47:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.90,0:47:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is chamomile even gonna fill anyone's stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.80,0:47:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For planting, plant it around here, not deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.40,0:47:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.24,0:47:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You first need to soak the hole with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.58,0:47:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.28,0:47:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can add the water later, you need to plant first.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.68,0:47:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong, wrong, wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.24,0:47:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sprinkle the fertilizer this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.74,0:47:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you add too much the insects will flock here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.22,0:47:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.60,0:47:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more daring with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.88,0:47:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.12,0:47:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to add just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.22,0:47:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You will definitely go wrong if you follow his advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.74,0:47:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.24,0:47:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.14,0:47:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.04,0:47:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Vinegar wood polish?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.56,0:47:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made from charcoal-roasted smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.80,0:47:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then then treated poultry manure is added to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.46,0:47:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.62,0:47:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.68,0:47:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for intruding so inadvertently and surprising you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.36,0:47:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.36,0:48:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been hard to work a land so raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.58,0:48:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know anything, so I had to study everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.78,0:48:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people moved here from the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.62,0:48:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but they always gave up and went back soon after.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.96,0:48:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Were there others as young as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.84,0:48:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, they were old men who had retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.32,0:48:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny how mental and weak they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.90,0:48:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That might just be me saying it but,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.56,0:48:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,this is no land that makes living off it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.94,0:48:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The drainage is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.50,0:48:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a ton of snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.26,0:48:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.86,0:48:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought you weren't one to socialize with your neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.66,0:48:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many young mothers around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.64,0:48:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's really reassuring to have one more of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.30,0:48:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.58,0:48:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.94,0:48:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You live off your savings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.52,0:48:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but they will soon run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.42,0:48:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to find a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.20,0:48:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone leaves their children at the \Nnursery school and goes far away to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.60,0:48:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of place is a “nursery school”?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.10,0:49:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't Yuki and Ame go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.14,0:49:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.30,0:49:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki wants to go to the nursery school!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.90,0:49:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.56,0:49:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.04,0:49:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.66,0:49:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I will! I will! I will! I will! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.94,0:49:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I will! I will! I will…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.48,0:49:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'LL GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.80,0:49:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to the nursery school, I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.56,0:49:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to! I want to! I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.38,0:49:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, hurry up and eat your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.26,0:49:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's about our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.52,0:49:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.24,0:49:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.70,0:49:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.10,0:49:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Y- Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.38,0:49:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana-chan, do you own a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.70,0:49:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, err... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.76,0:49:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.08,0:49:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, darling! It's a wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.70,0:49:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, well, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.68,0:49:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish, there are no more wolves in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.50,0:49:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shepherd mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.84,0:49:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Hana-chan? Ain't I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.84,0:49:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, ain't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.80,0:49:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The dog is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.64,0:49:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Nirasaki, good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.56,0:50:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.02,0:50:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you sociable today?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.78,0:50:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your clothes are just like your dog's.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.38,0:50:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.44,0:50:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Y- Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.54,0:50:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.84,0:50:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.98,0:50:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.08,0:50:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where grandpa Nirasaki is...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.82,0:50:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They were grown quite nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.02,0:50:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to everyone's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.28,0:50:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The roots on ours were damaged, so this will be very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.22,0:51:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean damaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.68,0:51:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A boar.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.94,0:51:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.20,0:51:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This much!?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.92,0:51:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those boars...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.18,0:51:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll thankfully accept these.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.62,0:51:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning, without making a noise, he dug everything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.14,0:51:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that this year he even went as far as going to Sakei's rice field.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.38,0:51:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is in exchange. It's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.94,0:51:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana-chan's field was the only one that the animals didn't damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.28,0:51:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a miracle on this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.88,0:51:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's a trick to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.52,0:51:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.06,0:51:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We would all like to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.82,0:51:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What does “trick” mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.58,0:51:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.66,0:51:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She is so lively, that Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.62,0:51:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,By any chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.70,0:51:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.12,0:51:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.74,0:51:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.14,0:51:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's in exchange for the potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.14,0:51:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a long time since we had any eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.70,0:51:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.94,0:51:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me if you run out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.26,0:51:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.50,0:51:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's SO cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.40,0:51:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.96,0:51:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.12,0:51:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's so big. I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.28,0:52:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.28,0:52:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from a guy who had it sitting in his shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.14,0:52:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.54,0:52:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.66,0:52:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides if we take it back the old man would be angry at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.98,0:52:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,“Old man”?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.54,0:52:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,“Hana-chan this”, “Hana-chan that”, it's getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.18,0:52:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He is totally in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.30,0:52:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's over 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.08,0:52:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But when he's looking out for someone, he gets everyone involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.48,0:52:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.04,0:52:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be saying things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.16,0:52:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.58,0:52:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally understand the reason why the field had to be bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.40,0:52:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.00,0:52:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.06,0:52:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you always smiling like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.50,0:52:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.26,0:53:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.14,0:53:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I moved here to escape from people's eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.30,0:53:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up getting a lot of help from everyone at the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.94,0:53:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hard at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.88,0:53:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but somehow it seems like I can keep on going.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.80,0:53:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.78,0:56:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,M- mo- mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.42,0:56:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.18,0:56:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, Ame is-!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.58,0:56:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,M- mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.68,0:56:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.50,0:57:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame! Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.68,0:57:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.54,0:57:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,M- o- mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.60,0:57:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.28,0:57:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.82,0:57:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.66,0:57:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.62,0:57:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.30,0:57:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes, Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.80,0:57:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.58,0:57:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.10,0:57:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame! Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.84,0:57:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.22,0:57:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.40,0:57:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom... It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.64,0:57:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.82,0:57:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.02,0:57:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a crested kingfisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.56,0:57:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a really beautiful crested kingfisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.52,0:58:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Today even I felt like catching one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.18,0:58:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.56,0:58:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was totally different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.08,0:58:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.04,0:58:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like I could do anything for a moment there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.16,0:58:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.48,0:58:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.52,0:58:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.14,0:58:31.64,Narration,,0,0,0,,Later my mother said that she had never been so scared in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.42,0:58:35.36,Narration,,0,0,0,,After that, Ame,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.68,0:58:38.12,Narration,,0,0,0,,turned into someone completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.06,0:58:46.24,Narration,,0,0,0,,When that long winter ended and spring approaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.24,0:58:50.38,Narration,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go to elementary school like everyone else, it was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.58,0:58:53.34,Narration,,0,0,0,,So, to persuade my mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.34,0:58:55.72,Narration,,0,0,0,,I started following every single order to the full extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.00,0:58:59.72,Narration,,0,0,0,,That ended up working and finally, I could go.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.72,0:59:00.46,Narration,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.98,0:59:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.26,0:59:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't become a wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.94,0:59:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.62,0:59:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.58,0:59:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can manage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.74,0:59:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do “Three presents, three octopuses”.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.30,0:59:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.96,0:59:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good luck charm so you don't become a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.74,0:59:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.22,0:59:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You do “Three presents, three octopuses”.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.62,0:59:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three..”
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.60,0:59:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,“Presents, three octopuses.”
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.74,0:59:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three presents, three octopuses”.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.88,0:59:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three presents, three octopuses”.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.64,0:59:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three presents, three octopuses”.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.60,0:59:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.14,0:59:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three presents, three octopuses”.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.72,0:59:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three presents, three octopuses”.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.58,0:59:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three presents, three octopuses”.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.08,1:00:03.44,Narration,,0,0,0,,It was the first time in my life I was surrounded by so many people.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.88,1:00:06.62,Narration,,0,0,0,,Even though I wanted to go so much,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.28,1:00:12.46,Narration,,0,0,0,,when I got there I was unsure if I could actually do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.38,1:00:16.24,Narration,,0,0,0,,But that was only at the start.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.88,1:00:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.42,1:00:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.70,1:00:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice trip, take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.70,1:00:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.04,1:00:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shino-chan! Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.30,1:00:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.56,1:00:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I saved you your seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.92,1:00:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.10,1:00:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,First Grade
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.08,1:00:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, who knows the answer to this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.04,1:00:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.04,1:00:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me! Me! Me! Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.82,1:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, no running!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.96,1:00:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.58,1:00:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.20,1:00:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.48,1:00:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.46,1:01:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you could do that!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.06,1:01:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.40,1:01:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.16,1:01:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.40,1:01:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Job offers – Part-time
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.50,1:01:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.90,1:01:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The nature observatory of the Niikawa's forest is looking for an assistant researcher.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.88,1:01:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Historic village's nature
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.90,1:01:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.16,1:01:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.52,1:01:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the nature observer, Tendo.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.90,1:01:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Niikawa's forest nature observatory.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.60,1:01:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for welcoming us here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.96,1:01:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A nature observer's job is not only to protect the forest,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.98,1:01:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,they study the environment, survey the field, and preserve the wild life.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.10,1:01:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,These three pillars are what we ask of volunteers while they're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.54,1:01:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The range of activities diverges and crosses over,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.80,1:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a specialist must be simultaneously proficient in all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.92,1:01:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we are taking applications for an\N assistant to the busy nature observers.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.36,1:01:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That is indeed the case.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.70,1:02:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The wage is pretty low, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.46,1:02:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future, you can aim to be a nature observer,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.60,1:02:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but the study required for that and\N training expenses are the only implications.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.34,1:02:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The hourly wage of a part-time high school student is best suited for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.76,1:02:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.04,1:02:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want the job?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.06,1:02:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.70,1:02:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you keep a wolf here...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.78,1:02:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a timber wolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.92,1:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He is quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.52,1:02:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of his age.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.22,1:02:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Board chairman, could you...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.24,1:02:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.02,1:02:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.16,1:02:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here because there's something I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.80,1:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy is the son of a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.48,1:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,His wolf father passed away.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.56,1:02:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I am his mother,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.22,1:02:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know how to raise a wolf child.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.02,1:03:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to become an adult wolf?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.16,1:03:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you tell me about the time you were raised in the woods?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.64,1:03:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.98,1:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A wealthy person got special permission to acquire and raise him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.70,1:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But when he died he left no caretakers, so they brought him to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.10,1:03:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he was originally born at a zoo in Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.36,1:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't a wild animal?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.36,1:03:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare to see wild wolves at zoos.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.54,1:03:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If one is born from breeding, it's taken as a foster child.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.38,1:03:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that, we take in hurt wild birds and raccoon dogs.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.82,1:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,After that we deal with healing them.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.24,1:03:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to commute there from now on,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.36,1:03:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but will you be okay doing it with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.70,1:04:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm working I'll teach you everything,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.98,1:04:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,about the mountains and nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.94,1:04:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I saw a real one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.94,1:04:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A wolf?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.74,1:04:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Was dad like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.56,1:04:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.72,1:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.50,1:04:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.16,1:04:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that guy looked very lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.06,1:04:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to meet my dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.40,1:04:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom wants to see him again, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.74,1:04:34.04,Narration,,0,0,0,,And with that, after my mom found herself a job,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.24,1:04:36.54,Narration,,0,0,0,,I underwent a big impact.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.38,1:04:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fumiko-chan, yours looks great.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.66,1:04:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours is better, Keno-chan.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.52,1:04:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a four-leafed clover.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.32,1:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.36,1:04:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.78,1:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.30,1:04:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.94,1:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.00,1:04:53.80,Narration,,0,0,0,,Just for fun I caught a rat snake and wrapped it around my arm
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.80,1:04:56.02,Narration,,0,0,0,,but there were no girls like me in school.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.02,1:04:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, this is my mother's jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.32,1:04:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.66,1:05:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She got this one on her last birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.38,1:05:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.22,1:05:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, show us your treasure chest!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.26,1:05:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.98,1:05:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is inside?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.48,1:05:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.72,1:05:13.28,Narration,,0,0,0,,There were no other girls
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.28,1:05:18.88,Narration,,0,0,0,,who would happily gather small animal bones and reptile dry skins besides me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.84,1:05:23.62,Narration,,0,0,0,,“Other girls didn't do these things”, I realized.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.62,1:05:25.82,Narration,,0,0,0,,I was so embarrassed that it got me anxious.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.98,1:05:29.88,Narration,,0,0,0,,I reached a decision:
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.88,1:05:33.92,Narration,,0,0,0,,From now on I would act as graceful and girly as I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.54,1:05:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.56,1:05:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm troubled with all seriousness!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.42,1:05:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You should do the things you feel like doing, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.30,1:05:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want people to think I'm a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.10,1:05:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have to help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.62,1:05:59.52,Narration,,0,0,0,,I remember I got really happy that my mother
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.52,1:06:01.70,Narration,,0,0,0,,started sewing a new dress just for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.00,1:06:05.62,Narration,,0,0,0,,Because of this I stopped feeling out of place in the middle of the class.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.62,1:06:08.30,Narration,,0,0,0,,I started getting along much better with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.30,1:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.76,1:06:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.88,1:06:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your clothes are really cute, Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.08,1:06:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.30,1:06:16.84,Narration,,0,0,0,,I say that this dress saved me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.66,1:06:21.28,Narration,,0,0,0,,Next year it was really hard to get Ame to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.70,1:06:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.26,1:06:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's “Three presents, three octopuses”.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.42,1:06:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The school is this way!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.70,1:06:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on entering school, first graders!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.24,1:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get along with your classmates, second graders!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.10,1:06:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in high-spirits, first graders!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.38,1:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for a perfect score, second graders!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.38,1:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get along with your friends, second graders!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.20,1:07:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Always with a smile, third graders.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.50,1:07:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember your good manners, third graders!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.88,1:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly up high with your friends,  fourth graders!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.26,1:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Always do your best, third graders!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.40,1:07:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.64,1:07:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ame-kun. Is today a holiday at school?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.94,1:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.84,1:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're ditching?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.70,1:07:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.42,1:07:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come here whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.02,1:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.36,1:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the research center.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.08,1:08:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you can also see a Mountain Frog that has a tail.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.04,1:08:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana-chan! Can you help us here?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.18,1:08:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Suure!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.02,1:08:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone, your attention.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.54,1:08:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you the new exchange student.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.40,1:08:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Fujii Souhei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.54,1:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.16,1:08:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Fujii. It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.26,1:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.02,1:08:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you have a pet dog?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.42,1:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.40,1:08:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you smell like a furry animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.04,1:08:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.92,1:08:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.12,1:08:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was pretty sure you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.90,1:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.12,1:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no. It's just this smell.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.24,1:08:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A smell? Of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.94,1:08:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.18,1:09:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is it...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.04,1:09:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, it's this one!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.26,1:09:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.08,1:09:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.72,1:09:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You come here, too. Souhei-kun is really funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.00,1:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to return this book.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.16,1:09:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.28,1:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She not always like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.48,1:09:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Yuki. About that...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.42,1:09:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, about that...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.42,1:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.92,1:09:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.16,1:09:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.54,1:09:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Be honest with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.62,1:09:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.76,1:09:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.36,1:09:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.86,1:09:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't like me because I'm an exchange student?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.96,1:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.90,1:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.28,1:09:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you avoiding me?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.64,1:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.30,1:10:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three presents, three octopus.”
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.20,1:10:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three presents, three octopus.”
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.16,1:10:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three..”
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.44,1:10:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.06,1:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.00,1:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three presents, three octopuses.”
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.62,1:10:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three presents, three octopuses.”
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.36,1:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three presents, three octopuses.”
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.94,1:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,“Three presents, three octopuses.”
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.36,1:10:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.16,1:10:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.94,1:10:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get any closer!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.00,1:10:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.26,1:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.84,1:10:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.10,1:10:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.28,1:10:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana-chan. Telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.60,1:10:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.66,1:10:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.78,1:11:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to call you in the middle of work.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.38,1:11:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how much blood he lost from his head?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.80,1:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just my ear.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.68,1:11:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.04,1:11:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what I ask her she doesn't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.42,1:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really hurt him?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.24,1:11:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you apologize to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.74,1:11:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.18,1:11:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.02,1:11:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.30,1:11:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no excuse for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.80,1:11:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Souhei-kun's mother
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.26,1:12:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,payed the doctor's expenses with the school's insurance, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.04,1:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if it had drained all the blood from my son's head?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.96,1:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if by some chance he becomes deaf in that ear?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.54,1:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a child does is a parent's responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.96,1:12:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Does taking out a loan or selling your house make up for that?!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.18,1:12:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at any rate that's not what happened, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.72,1:12:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And what makes you think that's the case?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.38,1:12:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't listen I'll have to...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.94,1:12:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A wolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.12,1:12:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a wolf that did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.20,1:12:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a wolf that did this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.64,1:12:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Souhei. What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.28,1:12:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Souhei...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.06,1:12:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Souhei?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.74,1:12:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't catch the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.36,1:12:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she has been different lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.06,1:12:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Yuki-chan would never do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.52,1:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that it was her.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.22,1:12:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So the teacher...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.10,1:13:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened with Souhei-kun?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.10,1:13:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He left early.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.42,1:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.76,1:13:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.98,1:13:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.94,1:13:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.18,1:13:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hurt him?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.04,1:13:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.76,1:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.74,1:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.10,1:13:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.82,1:13:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really her?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.38,1:13:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.14,1:13:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.84,1:13:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet down! Everyone quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.10,1:13:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.96,1:13:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The good luck charm; no matter how many times I repeated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.52,1:13:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They... should expel me already.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.18,1:13:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we be unable to live at that house anymore?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.34,1:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.00,1:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.14,1:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.90,1:13:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.02,1:13:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.28,1:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Souhei-kun?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.30,1:14:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A printed paper. From Souhei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.74,1:15:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,From Souhei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.00,1:15:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Souhei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.12,1:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Today she went to play at Shino-chan's house.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.72,1:15:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.88,1:15:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.64,1:15:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You must live pretty far away.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.96,1:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming here everyday.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.00,1:15:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like that Yuki is not going to school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.14,1:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You said, at that time,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.44,1:16:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,“A wolf did it”, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.22,1:16:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you mean by it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.12,1:16:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That was... I mean..
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.90,1:16:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not believe it, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.72,1:16:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For a moment there I'm pretty sure I saw a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.22,1:16:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as I noticed it, it hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.64,1:16:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I said that a wolf did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.20,1:16:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means it wasn't Yuki's fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.78,1:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone says I'm talking nonsense with that...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.14,1:16:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.00,1:16:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you one more question?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.92,1:16:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate wolves?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.48,1:16:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.08,1:16:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.76,1:17:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.76,1:17:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna see it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.90,1:17:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.34,1:17:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to touch it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.74,1:17:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.72,1:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Itches a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.38,1:17:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.92,1:17:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.94,1:17:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.00,1:17:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To my teacher's home.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.36,1:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is your teacher?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.68,1:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher is... My teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.50,1:17:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.58,1:17:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be okay on your own?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.06,1:17:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.52,1:17:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.52,1:17:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.68,1:17:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stay out late.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.06,1:17:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.40,1:17:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.56,1:17:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She went back to school today.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.40,1:18:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great. What about Ame-chan?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.30,1:18:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Some times he goes, some times not.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.32,1:18:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's also good for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.16,1:18:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys who don't go to school since elementary school are very promising.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.34,1:18:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Edison and I were like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.58,1:18:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he is talking nonsense again.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.86,1:18:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I remember, who lives up in the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.04,1:18:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountain?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.70,1:18:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame said that he was going to his teacher's place,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.90,1:18:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he meant the old man but...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.36,1:18:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.36,1:18:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone on the mountain during this busy farming season?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.10,1:18:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.44,1:18:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything about the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.70,1:18:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you would get along with older people...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.14,1:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time bring him here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.78,1:18:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank him for taking care of you, besides...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.18,1:18:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher doesn't meet with humans.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.06,1:18:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't go down to the village like the bears and boars.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.02,1:18:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess he might like to meet my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.32,1:19:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher is the master in charge of this whole mountain's territory.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.00,1:19:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for always taking care of Ame.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.20,1:22:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get in now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.24,1:22:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to bring Yuki to my teacher's place too.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.30,1:22:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm improving my hunting technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.42,1:22:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a trick to run at full speed in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.86,1:22:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also a way to read the terrain.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.78,1:22:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been studying a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.92,1:22:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like how to find streams and how to read the weather,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.92,1:22:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,also about territory and how to respect them.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.26,1:22:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.60,1:22:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.40,1:22:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And why don't you go to school anymore?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.82,1:22:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the mountain is much more fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.86,1:22:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many things I still have to learn there.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.74,1:22:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better not to learn those.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.18,1:22:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.98,1:22:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just start going to school!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.92,1:22:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.46,1:22:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.12,1:22:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.18,1:22:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're human.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.06,1:22:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're wolves.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.00,1:22:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided I'm never turning into a wolf again.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.54,1:22:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.46,1:22:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.36,1:22:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm human!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.50,1:22:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? I'm HUMAN!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.58,1:22:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.50,1:23:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're annoying asking "why, why".
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.38,1:23:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, you're a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.82,1:23:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you're a wolf,  you...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.98,1:23:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.84,1:23:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.28,1:23:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.00,1:23:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive you if you don't come to school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.18,1:23:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.08,1:23:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.26,1:23:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't go!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.04,1:23:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.72,1:23:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.70,1:23:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.56,1:23:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki! Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.52,1:23:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it you two!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.26,1:23:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Yuki! Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.20,1:24:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki! Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.36,1:24:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.40,1:24:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Yuki and Ame started walking on their separate paths.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.08,1:24:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of being hopeful like I should,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.18,1:25:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,why do I feel this uneasy?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.42,1:25:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, why?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.60,1:25:18.10,Narration,,0,0,0,,The last summer of my elementary school life,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.10,1:25:20.60,Narration,,0,0,0,,was full of many record-setting heavy rains.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.54,1:25:25.10,Narration,,0,0,0,,Ame started going to the mountain more frequently.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.22,1:25:27.46,Narration,,0,0,0,,Those heavy rains,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.46,1:25:31.30,Narration,,0,0,0,,would affect his teacher and the mountain flora and fauna.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.30,1:25:33.30,Narration,,0,0,0,,He seemed very worried about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.70,1:26:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.08,1:26:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been all this time?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.58,1:26:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.68,1:26:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll warm up the bath for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.00,1:26:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher... Hurt his leg and can't walk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.26,1:26:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He... might die soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.30,1:26:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has to take the place of my teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.88,1:26:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and carry on his duties.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.90,1:26:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.88,1:26:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go to the mountain anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.42,1:26:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? You're still only 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.04,1:26:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.06,1:26:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though a 10 year old wolf is an adult, you're...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.52,1:26:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.60,1:26:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go to the mountain anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.62,1:26:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your mom's... wish...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.22,1:27:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now. I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.50,1:27:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Shoot it in!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.62,1:27:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindo, shoot it!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.58,1:27:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, pass!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.76,1:27:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.84,1:27:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.50,1:27:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I overheard my parents talking about it...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.08,1:27:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.18,1:27:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Souhei-kun's mother...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.64,1:27:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She is getting married.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.88,1:27:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.76,1:27:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.92,1:27:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.18,1:27:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Souhei-kun will get a new father.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.58,1:27:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.28,1:27:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, Souhei-kun doesn't know anything about it, they said.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.94,1:27:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.82,1:27:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.54,1:27:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.32,1:27:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.56,1:27:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! It got in! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.30,1:27:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the score now?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.70,1:27:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.72,1:27:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, shoot...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.90,1:28:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.04,1:28:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Today the weather will be great the whole morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.36,1:28:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but from the evening to late tonight a strong rain is forecast..
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.88,1:28:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's humid today.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.12,1:28:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.62,1:28:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay home today.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.64,1:28:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.52,1:28:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.86,1:29:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll miss the bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.60,1:29:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.40,1:29:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come too.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.10,1:29:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.38,1:29:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.56,1:29:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...after a nice day it will rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.56,1:29:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning might strike in some places.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.66,1:29:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For the southwest, sun followed by rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.72,1:29:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.96,1:29:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.64,1:29:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.30,1:29:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do a question about the distance a\N swallow can fly nonstop for three whole hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.92,1:29:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,First do you all understand what it means if we say it moves at a 70km/h speed?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.60,1:29:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,70km/h.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.26,1:29:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that this is the distance he \Ncan cover after flying for one whole hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.44,1:29:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So if he flew for one hour he would have covered a distance of 70 km...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.42,1:29:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The front that's stagnated in Japan's sea heads south.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.92,1:29:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The condition of the atmosphere above the \Nprefecture area has suddenly become unstable.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.60,1:30:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,After this, expect locally extraordinarily\N heavy rains accompanied with thunder and gales.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.02,1:30:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Precipitation is estimated at 70 mm an \Nhour on the plains, depending on the location.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.90,1:30:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Areas with lots of mountains are estimated to surpass 100 mm an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.90,1:30:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.24,1:30:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sit down. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.18,1:30:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it seems a storm is coming,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.74,1:30:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we're canceling the classes for this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.00,1:30:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.62,1:31:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone call their parents to come pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.98,1:31:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in contact with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.06,1:31:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Until they arrive everyone should be gathered and waiting at the gym.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.12,1:31:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A power outage?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.86,1:31:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.54,1:32:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, I'm going right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.70,1:32:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame. Let's go bring Yuki home together.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.60,1:32:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.12,1:32:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.18,1:32:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.88,1:32:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.98,1:32:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.52,1:32:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.76,1:32:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Ame?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.38,1:32:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.02,1:33:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Takahiro...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.42,1:33:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.76,1:33:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.82,1:33:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.44,1:33:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alps are 10,000-
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.32,1:33:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Our father is taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.62,1:33:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.04,1:33:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.74,1:33:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If we have to stay here at school for the night,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.96,1:33:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we will play cards the whole night.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.64,1:33:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cards?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.68,1:33:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna play!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.40,1:33:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.58,1:33:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like camping.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.72,1:33:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go pick up the cards in class.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.40,1:33:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.02,1:33:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how to play cards?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.92,1:33:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I only know how to play Old Maid.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.56,1:33:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.64,1:33:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.28,1:33:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shino!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.06,1:33:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, father.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.58,1:34:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.14,1:34:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, the storm is really strong, gee.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.32,1:34:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, want me to take you too?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.64,1:34:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Come with us, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.94,1:34:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.62,1:34:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.02,1:34:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the offer,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.24,1:34:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think my mother is on her way already.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.86,1:34:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for restraint.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.62,1:34:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.94,1:34:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be troublesome if I cross my mom without meeting her.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.40,1:34:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.80,1:34:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.64,1:34:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.94,1:34:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.12,1:34:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.58,1:34:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.10,1:34:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.90,1:35:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.38,1:35:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.42,1:35:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou-chan... He's taking too long...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.36,1:35:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.04,1:35:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Did Yuki-chan go back already?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.06,1:35:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone, pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.68,1:35:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who are left will be taken home by the school's driver.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.36,1:35:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your backpacks and gather here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.92,1:36:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.08,1:36:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.72,1:36:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.68,1:36:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.08,1:36:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.22,1:37:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.62,1:37:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.76,1:37:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.14,1:37:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.78,1:38:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You were taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.38,1:38:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What? They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.32,1:38:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone went home already.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.16,1:38:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was the only one nobody came to take home.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.76,1:38:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if something happened to my mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.78,1:38:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.72,1:38:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hang around.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.42,1:38:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.94,1:38:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.28,1:38:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If they are not going to take us home, what will we do?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.96,1:38:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather live here at school.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.64,1:38:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.98,1:38:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We can sleep at the infirmary when the night comes, can't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.38,1:38:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about food?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.32,1:38:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have the leftovers from lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.32,1:38:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if nobody ever comes to take you home?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.32,1:38:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you live here forever?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.86,1:38:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I would find a job. Delivering newspapers or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.60,1:38:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a kid. They wouldn't hire you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.56,1:38:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd lie about my age. I would say I'm in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.60,1:38:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look like a middle school student?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.70,1:38:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.76,1:38:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.74,1:39:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become an adult faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.92,1:39:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.90,1:40:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.52,1:40:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.38,1:40:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you trembling in cold?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.94,1:40:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't come back...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.36,1:40:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cry...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.32,1:40:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.04,1:40:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Must... Protect you...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.22,1:40:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... Protect you...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.00,1:41:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anybody there?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.50,1:41:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.70,1:41:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.38,1:41:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are we hiding?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.90,1:41:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.72,1:41:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.64,1:41:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it absorbed everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.92,1:41:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we'll really be able to keep living here in secrecy...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.04,1:41:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If our parents don't come we can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.00,1:42:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.14,1:42:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your mother will come.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.98,1:42:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.12,1:42:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? After all...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.94,1:42:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother... She got married.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.14,1:42:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.72,1:42:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When that baby is born she won't need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.22,1:42:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after she was that worried about you...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.60,1:42:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually pretty fine with that,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.64,1:42:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave home now,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.64,1:42:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,become a boxer or a wrestler,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.88,1:42:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and live like a lone wolf.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.36,1:42:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Think I can do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.00,1:42:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou-chan, you'll get hurt right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.94,1:42:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're frail.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.88,1:42:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll train.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.66,1:42:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll train and live on my own.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.96,1:42:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou-chan..
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.42,1:43:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could be like you,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.52,1:43:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,being able to smile even when talking about my true self.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.88,1:43:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.22,1:43:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The wolf that hurt you that one time...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.70,1:43:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.30,1:43:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.30,1:43:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That has been hurting me until now.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.76,1:43:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. All along.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.38,1:43:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tell your secret to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.16,1:43:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't say it to anyone, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.12,1:44:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.54,1:44:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying. Those are raindrops.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.32,1:44:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.82,1:44:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame! Where have you gone to?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.38,1:44:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.16,1:44:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.40,1:45:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.14,1:45:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's hurry back and bring Yuki home...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.42,1:45:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.40,1:45:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.42,1:45:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been working hard all this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.32,1:45:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.26,1:45:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.58,1:45:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.15,1:45:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.08,1:45:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've raised the kids pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.22,1:45:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.30,1:45:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I made only mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.82,1:45:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.20,1:45:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But both Ame and Yuki grew up nicely.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.76,1:45:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Because...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.00,1:45:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame is...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.06,1:46:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Ame is missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.76,1:46:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.18,1:46:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame is fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.10,1:46:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.20,1:46:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fine. He's an adult already.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.98,1:46:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,An adult?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.94,1:46:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He found a world he belongs in.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.24,1:47:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.92,1:47:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.22,1:47:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.36,1:47:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I haven't done anything for you yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.66,1:47:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Still not yet...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.64,1:47:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.84,1:47:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.66,1:47:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.82,1:47:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.78,1:47:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.12,1:48:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.52,1:48:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.62,1:48:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.00,1:48:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Live your life!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.22,1:49:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.76,1:49:31.92,Narration,,0,0,0,,My mother said she would never forget that morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.48,1:49:37.22,Narration,,0,0,0,,The washed beech leaves, and the washed spiderwebs,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.04,1:49:39.26,Narration,,0,0,0,,and the washed sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.20,1:49:43.76,Narration,,0,0,0,,Everything was reflecting the sunlight so brightly.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.70,1:49:49.24,Narration,,0,0,0,,It was like the whole world had been reborn anew in a single night,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.64,1:49:52.50,Narration,,0,0,0,,that's what my mother thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.72,1:50:23.14,Narration,,0,0,0,,The following year, to live in the middle school's dormitory,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.14,1:50:24.90,Narration,,0,0,0,,I left home.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.90,1:50:30.90,Narration,,0,0,0,,When my mother, who had raised us for 12 years, looks back on that,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.86,1:50:36.16,Narration,,0,0,0,,says that it completely feels like a fairytale, and laughs.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.94,1:50:39.36,Narration,,0,0,0,,Very fulfilling,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.24,1:50:42.16,Narration,,0,0,0,,like looking on a peak very far away,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.20,1:50:48.06,Narration,,0,0,0,,that smile on her face makes me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.16,1:51:03.00,Narration,,0,0,0,,My mother still quietly lives in that house on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.48,1:52:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,